{"type":"message","id":"ce26c876","parentId":"9fac33f0","timestamp":"2026-05-13T06:05:10.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No existing Unity process with RunHotUpdatePipeline. Good, we can proceed.\n\nNow let me start the Unity process in batch mode. I'll use Start-Process with -NoNewWindow -Wait -PassThru. But since I need to monitor progress while it runs, I should run it in the background and periodically check logs.\n\nLet me start the process as a background job so I can monitor logs while it runs.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没有找到正在运行的 Unity 热更流水线进程，可以开始执行。\n\n现在启动 Unity 批处理模式热更流水线，并持续监控日志。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_aIDLN710k4mddN7PwRB95654","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$unityPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"\n$projectPath = \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\"\n$logFile = \"$projectPath\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\n$method = \"YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline\"\n\n# 移除旧的日志文件\nRemove-Item $logFile -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\nWrite-Output \"UNITY_STARTED\"\nWrite-Output \"日志文件: $logFile\"\n\n$psi = New-Object System.Diagnostics.ProcessStartInfo\n$psi.FileName = $unityPath\n$psi.Arguments = \"-quit -batchmode -projectPath `\"$projectPath`\" -executeMethod $method -logFile `\"$logFile`\"\"\n$psi.UseShellExecute = $false\n$psi.RedirectStandardOutput = $true\n$psi.RedirectStandardError = $true\n\n$proc = [System.Diagnostics.Process]::Start($psi)\n\nWrite-Output \"PID: $($proc.Id)\"\n$proc.Id","timeout":15,"background":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":90,"output":435,"cacheRead":10752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11277,"cost":{"input":0.000012600000000000001,"output":0.0001218,"cacheRead":0.000301056,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000435456}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778652305182,"responseId":"ad873a69-a99f-4245