{"type":"message","id":"877d992a","parentId":"d46b334c","timestamp":"2026-05-13T06:09:08.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the results:\n\n1. **Asset Bundle Building** - All 3 packages built successfully:\n   - DefaultPackage/1.1.058 (14.1 kb)\n   - CommonPackage/1.1.057 (207.8 kb)\n   - SoloPackage/1.1.055 (no size mentioned)\n\n2. **CDN Upload Step (上传CDN)**:\n   - \"2026/5/13 14:07:44:begin 'Excute Pipline:上传CDN'\"\n   - It tried to use git but got \"fatal: not a git repository\" - this seems like it was trying to use the CDN git repo at `D:/cdn_solo`\n   - There's a \"System.Net.WebException: The remote server returned an error: (404) Not Found.\" - this might be expected if it's checking if a file exists on CDN\n   - It created Server.json and GFServer.json at D:/cdn_solo/update/Android/Test1/1.0.41/Config/AB1/\n   - It set up the local test environment at D:/cdn_solo/update/Android/Test1/1.0.41\n   - \"2026/5/13 14:07:45:end 'Excute Pipline:上传CDN', Consuming time:1.4280443s\"\n\n3. After the CDN upload step completed, the pipeline continued to execute more steps (ExecuteStep called many times), and then Unity showed the refresh and shutdown sequence.\n\nThe log shows the CDN step completed in 1.43 seconds. The 404 error might be normal (checking if a file exists before uploading). The local test environment was set up successfully.\n\nBut wait - it says \"Excute Pipline:上传CDN\" with garbled Chinese characters (the log seems to have encoding issues). The step completed with \"end\". But I also see \"fatal: not a git repository\" which means it couldn't push to the CDN git repo because it couldn't find the git repo at `D:/cdn_solo`.\n\nLet me check what happened in more detail around the CDN step. The flow appears to be:\n1. Git pull (failed - not a git repository)\n2. Download CDN file (got 404)\n3. Create Server.json and GFServer.json\n4. Set up local test environment\n5. Step completed\n\nThe pipeline seems to have completed without throwing an error (the ExecuteContinued at line 239 indicates it continued to the next step), but the CDN upload step may not have actually uploaded anything to a remote CDN. However, based on the \"本地测试模式\" (local test mode) message, this seems to be using a local test environment rather than actually uploading to a remote CDN.\n\nActually wait - it's calling \"PipelineHotUpdate\" which is the hot update pipeline that organizes files for CDN. The \"本地测试模式\" means it's in local test mode, so it prepared the files locally rather than uploading to a remote CDN.\n\nLet me check the Unity exit code and overall status more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_hT6nbIPNjJBLtikFYp3r6969","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$logFile = \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\n\n# Get Unity exit code from process record  \n$p = Get-CimInstance Win32_Process -Filter \"ProcessId=20776\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nWrite-Output \"=== Unity退出代码记录 ===\"\nGet-WmiObject Win32_Process -Filter \"ProcessId=20776\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n# Check for errors and exceptions in the log\nWrite-Output \"=== 搜索Exception/Error/fatal ===\"\nSelect-String -Path $logFile -Pattern 'Exception|Error|fatal|error|Exception|exited with code|Exit code' | Select-Object -Last 15\n\n# Check if pipeline completed successfully - look for end markers\nWrite-Output \"=== 搜索流水线结束标记 ===\"\nSelect-String -Path $logFile -Pattern 'Excute Pipline|Pipeline.*end|流水线.*完成|Pipeline.*Complete|RunHotUpdatePipeline.*end|Building complete|Build.*complete' | Select-Object -Last 15\n\n# Check the area between CDN end and Unity shutdown (lines 660537-end)\nWrite-Output \"=== CDN步骤完成后的日志 ===\"\nGet-Content $logFile -Tail $($(Get-Content $logFile).Count - 660537) | Select-Object -First 30\n\n# Also check if Unity exited with error by looking for explicit exit codes\nWrite-Output \"=== 搜索Unity退出 ===\"\nSelect-String -Path $logFile -Pattern 'Exiting|Shutdown|退出|Exit|exited' | Select-Object -Last 10","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":7822,"output":1082,"cacheRead":30208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39112,"cost":{"input":0.00109508,"output":0.00030296,"cacheRead":0.000845824,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002243864}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778652533426,"responseId":"704be610-cfdc-4428-9688-2049be02f62f"}}
