{"type":"message","id":"d909a212","parentId":"852e8778","timestamp":"2026-05-13T06:09:34.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me summarize the results:\n\nThe pipeline had two steps:\n1. **打资源 (Build Assets)** - Completed successfully at 14:07:44, took 124.04 seconds\n2. **上传CDN (Upload CDN)** - Began at 14:07:44, ended at 14:07:45, took 1.43 seconds\n\nHowever, the \"上传CDN\" step had issues:\n- \"fatal: not a git repository\" - couldn't find the CDN git repo at D:/cdn_solo\n- \"System.Net.WebException: The remote server returned an error: (404) Not Found.\" - this was likely from trying to download a file from the remote CDN server\n- It set up local test environment at D:/cdn_solo/update/Android/Test1/1.0.41\n\nAfter the pipeline steps completed, Unity went through a refresh (importing assets), then shutdown normally with \"AcceleratorClientConnectionCallback - disconnected\", \"Cleanup mono\", \"Found no leaked weakptrs\", etc.\n\nThe pipeline execution appears to have completed all its steps. The CDN upload step, while it encountered a 404 error, seems to have been handled gracefully (it was in \"本地测试模式\" - local test mode) and didn't crash the pipeline.\n\nThe Unity process exited cleanly (with no error messages in the shutdown). Let me try to determine the exit code.\n\nActually, looking at the output from the first search, the pipeline steps:\n1. \"Excute Pipline:打资源(打资源前需确认宏正确)\" - ENDED at 14:07:44, took 124.04s\n2. \"Excute Pipline:上传CDN\" - BEGAN at 14:07:44, ENDED at 14:07:45, took 1.43s\n\nBoth steps started and ended, which means the pipeline completed execution. The pipeline was launched with `-quit` flag, so Unity automatically exits when done.\n\nThe Unity process's exit code would tell us if it was successful. Since the process record shows normal shutdown (no crash, clean mono cleanup, no leaked weakptrs), it's very likely the exit code was 0.\n\nLet me check one more thing - whether there's any explicit failure indication in the log after the CDN step completed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"两步流水线都执行完毕。让我确认最终状态。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_AkNa0m1mLAsp1SkdiHO31266","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$logFile = \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\n\n# Check what happened right after CDN ended (lines around 660537-660600)\nWrite-Output \"=== CDN 完成后的日志 (line 660537+) ===\"\nGet-Content $logFile | Select-Object -Skip 660537 | Select-Object -First 60\n\n# Brief summary search\nWrite-Output \"=== 流水线关键信息汇总 ===\"\nGet-Content $logFile | Select-String -Pattern '构建成功|end .*Pipline|begin .*Pipline|Complete build|HotUpdate.*本地测试'","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2207,"output":719,"cacheRead":39168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42094,"cost":{"input":0.00030898000000000004,"output":0.00020132,"cacheRead":0.001096704,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001607004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778652563755,"responseId":"25ca26fc-80fa-4ae5-b3d0-6c99ccf81949"}}
